snippet.title: Dreamcast Longplay [008] Bangai-O
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played By: ScHlAuChi

The Dreamcast version of Bangai-O is an updated remake of the N64 original!
Unfortunately there are some small graphical glitches, like a visible grid during super-attacks and some small sound glitches! -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
